cs.CR, cs.CY, cs.SI, cs.SE, cs.DL

This paper focuses on the identification and characterization of cryptocurrency exchange scams, which involves the security and privacy of digital assets (cs.CR) and the use of technology to facilitate financial transactions (cs.CY). The paper also involves data analysis and machine learning techniques to identify and classify the scams (cs.SI, cs.SE), as well as the use of typosquatting generation techniques (cs.DL).
